Baju Streetwear
Streetwear fashion is a clothing style
that is heavily influenced by urbanites, youth culture and hip-hop. This can be seen in relaxed casual clothing such as oversized t-shirts, hoodies and sneakers. Streetwear
designs often feature bold graphic elements, such as large logos and photography. And it is often said to be
a form of self-expression.
